# LIANA cached resources data table
# Four tab-separated columns:
# value	name	description	path
#
# This file is populated automatically by data_manager_liana_resources.
# Each path is a directory named from <name> and containing <value>.tsv.
#
# Example entries created by the Data Manager:
# consensus	Consensus	Consensus ligand-receptor database	/galaxy/data/liana-db/Consensus
# hcop_human_mouse	HCOP Human-Mouse	HCOP ortholog mapping from human to mouse	/galaxy/data/liana-db/HCOP Human-Mouse
# metalinks_all	Metalinks All	All Metalinks metabolite-protein edges	/galaxy/data/liana-db/Metalinks All
